Gall FORREST v. UNITED STATES. No. 7443. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. July 10, 1934. I Fred Patterson, of Honolulu, T. H., for appellant, ' Sanford B. D. Wood, TJ. S. Atty., and Wilson C. Moore, Asst. U. S. Atty., both of Honolulu, T. H.

Before WILBUR, SAWTELLE, and GARRECHT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
